{"tid":1920784,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「武漢肺炎」伊朗第一副總統都中招緊急隔離","createTime":"2020-03-11T16:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T03:07:42.000Z","uid":111993,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5eff961b2ee8885f42d8eca3df0c72c685d47883","tid":1920784,"uid":111993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"伊朗半官方媒體今（11）日證實，繼伊朗女性副總統馬蘇梅．埃布特卡（Masoumeh Ebtekar）確診後，第一副總統賈汗吉里（Eshaq Jahangiri）確診感染新型冠狀病毒，是目前伊朗國內與全球確診的最高層級官員，正與其他武漢肺炎患者一樣接受隔離治療。<br />\n據了解，伊朗「副總統」職務是伊朗《憲法》第124條規定的官職，由總統指定，負責領導與總統事務相關的組織，副總統的人數不定，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">列在第一位的被稱為「第一副總統」</span></strong>，伊朗從2009年7月到現在同時有12位副總統，其中以第一副總統最為重要，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在總統缺席的情況下，第一副總統</span></span>得以領導內閣會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3096852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3096852&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=d1eadee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3096852&h=30fa4279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3096852</a>"},{"pid":"6078ab0fc461a44a649ce0798352f9e9ffd4f765","tid":1920784,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"伊朗有核彈都冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n俾隊友teamkill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b0bb9c9f9728bb5dcc1e064a5ae40e91f8e3c0","tid":1920784,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f76dbb42d20